  "title": "The 2023 Private Equity Market Outlook: Aditya Raina and Laura White",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>StepStone Group- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2023-02-14T14:54:32+00:00\" title=\"Tuesday, February 14, 2023 - 14:54\">Tue, 02/14/2023 - 14:54</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">The 2023 Private Equity Market Outlook: Aditya Raina and Laura White</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/content/images/33721/featured-image/RPM-New-Thumbnail-.png\" height=\"367\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/content/images/33721/featured-image/RPM-New-Thumbnail-.png\" width=\"873\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>In this episode of RPM, <a href=\"https://www.stepstonegroup.com/members/aditya-raina/\" style=\"color:#96A700\">Aditya Raina</a> and <a href=\"https://www.stepstonegroup.com/members/laura-krivacek/\" style=\"color:#96A700\">Laura White</a>, two members of our Private Equity team, join co-host <a href=\"https://www.stepstonegroup.com/members/maribel-yoo/\" style=\"color:#96A700\">Maribel Yoo</a> to discuss StepStone’s 2023 outlook for private equity. They discuss:</p><ul><li>Key market observations and its impact on the PE fundraising environment (0:55);</li><li>PE transaction activity (2:54);</li><li>Secondary market opportunity for the PE asset class (9:46);</li><li>ESG considerations and impact investing in PE (12:40); and</li><li>Opportunities across market cycles (17:39)</li></ul><p>Read the transcript .</p><p>RPM is available on <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/rpm-reflections-on-private-markets/id1537055419\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#96A700\" target=\"_blank\">Apple Podcasts</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/1xZBHwyP2Bx6RRkMJKXOaP\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#96A700\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a>, <a href=\"https://www.stitcher.com/podcast/rpm-reflections-on-private-markets?refid=stpr\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#96A700\" target=\"_blank\">Stitcher</a>—anywhere you normally get your podcasts. Subscribe today!</p>\n<div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/Frame%20366%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href